messages.message: When creating a schema and adding a field, the `add to schema` button doesn’t do anything.

I think this is because the document is too long. We’re putting in an error message.

maybe when we update the error handling for this, we should block the user from even getting to this point of adding new fields. cc: @Arjun
@Eric Han what is the max page length? I’ve cut down the pdf to be 7 pages. There’s not much text on it and still get the same result.
I will look into this to make sure this is in fact the issue but @Seth from the looks of it that document has more text than what I’ve seen accepted
